data.title: Withdrawal Agreement of the UK of Great Britain and Northern Ireland from the EU and the European Atomic Energy Community: opening statement by Guy VERHOFSTADT (RE, BE), EP Brexit Steering Group coord
data.meta_description: During the plenary session (29-30 January 2020) in Brussels, Guy VERHOFSTADT (RE, BE), EP Brexit Steering Group coordinator, makes a statement during the debate on the withdrawal Agreement of the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland from the EU and the European Atomic Energy Community.
